sections.heading: home or mobile home; deemed real property
sections.text: For purposes of a bankruptcy plan under 11 U.S.C. chapter 13, a manufactured home or a mobile home shall be deemed real property under subdivision (b)(2) of 11 U.S.C. 1322, as such section existed on July 18, 2008.SourceLaws 2008, LB953, ยง 1.
